Agboola Fahod Ireoluwa (born 01st of December), known by his nickname  G_Fahod but popularly called Fahod, is a Nigerian citizen from Osogbo, Osun State. He speaks mostly  in Yoruba, his native tongue
In 2015, he released his ApplicationFAHOD, his follow-up Team, was released under his label imprint Rolling Diamond
